item.title: Enigma - Return To Innocence
item.description:
Love
devotion
Feeling
emotion
Don’t be afraid
to be weak
Don’t be too proud
to be strong
Just look into
your heart my friend
That will be the
return to yourself
The return to
innocence-

innocence
If you want then
start to laugh
If you must

Be yourself
don’t hide
Just believe
in destiny
